title: rpgitem list 显示问题
author: MinEvil
txt_content: 我输入了/rpgitem list就显示/rpgitem help terms [Strin]           Shows commands and help for commands that contain the search terms [Terms]   怎么解决？

replies.author: 莫愁123
replies.txt_content: 请把RPG_Items文件夹打开，打开locale文件夹，删除里面所有文件，然后打开RPG_Items的config文件，找到localeDownload和autoupdate这两项，把这两项都改为false，然后保存，重启服务器即可。望采纳！
